          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1682354434037-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>soft cheese</strong>, <strong>lemon zest </strong>(not sure about citrus? Try using less!), <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped parsley</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) and give everything a good stir until the soft cheese has melted</p><p>Chop the <strong>lemon[s]</strong> into wedges</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1682354441645-x200.jpg",
